604
00:28:36,420 --> 00:28:38,280
you arranged his books together.

605
00:28:38,650 --> 00:28:39,660
Wait.

606
00:28:41,980 --> 00:28:43,810
Have you read this book?

607
00:28:45,690 --> 00:28:47,300
The Disappearing Zoo

