609
00:28:49,380 --> 00:28:50,780
It's worth a place

610
00:28:50,780 --> 00:28:52,380
on the most noticeable spot.

611
00:28:54,900 --> 00:28:56,740
But the truth is,

612
00:28:57,380 --> 00:28:58,620
nobody buys

613
00:28:58,620 --> 00:28:59,860
his books.

614
00:29:01,530 --> 00:29:04,420
