645
00:30:09,580 --> 00:30:10,970
Who says no one buys his books?

646
00:30:10,970 --> 00:30:12,980
I'll buy, I'll buy all of them.

647
00:30:12,980 --> 00:30:13,980
All of them?

648
00:30:13,980 --> 00:30:14,930
Yes.

649
00:30:16,540 --> 00:30:17,940
She is your fan?

