00:30:23,610 --> 00:30:24,490
That's true.

653
00:30:24,700 --> 00:30:26,900
She didn't even like you.

654
00:30:28,660 --> 00:30:30,330
Don't go overboard.

655
00:30:30,580 --> 00:30:31,420
Come on.

