699
00:32:23,980 --> 00:32:25,260
But you are asking for more,

700
00:32:25,260 --> 00:32:27,020
I can't approve it.

701
00:32:27,020 --> 00:32:27,980
Chief Editor Yu.

702
00:32:27,980 --> 00:32:29,860
I want to come to work.

